  <Fragment slot="headline">How Old Am I Exactly? Age Calculator Guide</Fragment>

  <p>Most people know their age in years. Fewer people know their exact age in years, months, and days.</p>
  <p>An age calculator can tell you much more than your age in years. It can also show total days lived, your next birthday, and the day of the week you were born.</p>

  <h2>How Exact Age Is Calculated</h2>
  <p>Exact age is based on the difference between your date of birth and a target date, usually today.</p>
  <p>That means a good calculator needs to account for different month lengths, leap years, and whether your birthday has already passed this year.</p>

  <h2>Why Manual Age Math Can Be Tricky</h2>
  <p>Age is not just current year minus birth year. If the birthday has not happened yet this year, the result changes.</p>

  <h2>What an Age Calculator Can Tell You</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Exact age in years, months, and days</li>
    <li>Total days lived</li>
    <li>Total hours or minutes lived</li>
    <li>The weekday you were born</li>
    <li>How many days remain until your next birthday</li>
  </ul>

